title: Ukraine Needs US to End War, Lithuania's Leader Says
description:
President Gitanas Nauseda of Lithuania talks about diplomatic relations with the United States, security in Europe and ending the war in Ukraine. He speaks to Bloomberg's Oliver Crook.

(Video has been edited to remove misstatement by Lithuanian President Gitanas Nauseda) (Source: Bloomberg)
